{"tid":1860040,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"唔想醫護人員送頭，麻煩你哋幫忙簽埋佢！","createTime":"2020-02-03T12:45:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-07T17:39:27.000Z","uid":322412,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c209faf421279bade4b54d0bbeeb35f246a146fc","tid":1860040,"uid":322412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T12:45:35.000Z","msg":"請支持醫護前線一齊罷！ <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n📢民主黨發起全港簽名運動<br />\n支持醫護 封關救港 禁止內地人來港<br />\n<br />\n✅ 網上聯署連結: shorturl.at/iHSVZ<br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎襲港，內地確診個案已經突破一萬大關，全中國擴散，香港亦已經超過14個確診個案。封關是阻止疫情擴散的重中之重的必須手段。<br />\n<br />\n內地患者源源不絕來港求醫，醫療系統無可能應付全國需求。林鄭拒封關，醫護系統爆煲，香港人人自危。醫護人員發動罷工要求封關，是保護港人下迫於無奈的一步。<br />\n<br />\n因此，我們要求政府：<br />\n<br />\n1. 支持醫護人員訴求，即時封關，於關口採取嚴厲管制入境措施，禁止內地人來港；及<br />\n<br />\n2. 提供足夠口罩及防護裝備給醫護人員，前線公務員及市民，並制訂措施禁止商人抬價。<br />\n#民主黨 #撐醫護 #罷工 #封關 #聯署 #林卓延<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KyNgP2Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKyNgP2Y.jpg&h=35596f0c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"23dc97b321f14312781da940917015adc62b0853","tid":1860040,"uid":322412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T17:39:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fY9cc2B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfY9cc2B.jpg&h=bea723c5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8cTTGVW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8cTTGVW.jpg&h=abdf49e5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vWUWEHC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvWUWEHC.jpg&h=7c7c304c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/02/08/013858_19046e878dec901758630df6b2b993b3.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F02%2F08%2F013858_19046e878dec901758630df6b2b993b3.jpeg&h=c5509adc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/02/08/013859_c16d9734825b93d